reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works as advertised, and longer cord!
reviews.reviewText: Actually is a fast charger (plugged my old one in to verify), charging time we're identical. Plus longer cord!Only thing i didn't notice was it's a usb-c to usb-c cord, so you can't plug it into an older model laptop, or an airport/hotel charger without your wall adapter piece, but that's minor!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best super charging cord I've owned
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this charger set back in November of 2021. I lost one along the way, so I mainly used the one. A few days ago it finally stopped working. In defense of the product, I think it stopped working from it being continuous bent at one side of the USB that it might have disconnected wires. None the less, this is the best super charger I've ever owned. Although I'm not sure if the product is any different than when I ordered it.
